oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Warner Mack Job No. 38602
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 3120) for an order placed by Warner Mack for 2 orders of 100 two color jumbos and 4 half tone cuts for a performance at the High School Auditorium in LaFaollette, Tennessee on July 29, and the V. F. W. Auditorium in Greeneville, Tennessee on July 30. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
